{"tid":1545721,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"惠譽將香港信貸評級由AA+降至AA　展望負面","createTime":"2019-09-06T04:20:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-06T05:41:28.000Z","uid":50457,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"19b22003c324294b401da48d22c86468f3583ecd","tid":1545721,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T04:20:58.000Z","msg":"國際評級機構惠譽將香港信貸評級由AA+下調至AA，前景展望負面，並預測今年香港實際GDP增長為零，而2020年則增長1.2%。<br />\n<br />\n該行又指，最近港府推出一連串財政紓緩措施，以及財政收入將會遜於預期，故相信今年財政預算盈餘會收窄至近乎零。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20190906/mobile/bkn-20190906120248116-0906_00842_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Ffinance%2F20190906%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20190906120248116-0906_00842_001.html&d=qjQisgq6tteJ1Wb%2FuF84H0YZmLIq74JPLN0FyuDKESI%3D&h=36d8b9a1\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20190906/mobile/bkn-20190906120248116-0906_00842_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"17a43e48fe9439be19703ad9c450ad67c3d7f3ec","tid":1545721,"uid":14918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T04:21:28.000Z","msg":"沒事儿沒事儿"},{"pid":"33200d17fb57070792d2d012d1c73990be49a5c3","tid":1545721,"uid":89225,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T04:22:02.000Z","msg":"深圳要取代香港喎。香港評級應該要低過大陸啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9aff806f3a2cc5361b479b708f707a7c517e819","tid":1545721,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T04:22:13.000Z","msg":"[行動post] 肯入黎睇9.7點樣揸機場輸精管未 | LIHKG <br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1</a> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/reLz9Yb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FreLz9Yb.jpg&h=bc5ea362&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VeJJ3id.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=htt